pedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burton_Snowboards\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an impressive and penalty-free performance\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 742}, {\"ngram\": \"her second medal\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That saw Collett, who almost died after a bad fall in 2013, become the first British woman to win an individual eventing medal since Kristina Cook in 2008.\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristina_Cook\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kristina Cook\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristina_Cook\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristina_Cook\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Collett\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"a bad fall\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"the first British woman\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"an individual eventing medal\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB have become the major player in the world of equestrian in recent years and Collett admits the intense competition to make the Olympic team made her 'a bit sad to be British' before her place in Paris was confirmed.\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1018, \"end\": 1025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9998737359408386, \"rank\": 0.00012553617592230286, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1071, \"end\": 1081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9937507131268335, \"rank\": 0.006288566739451239, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}, {\"begin\": 1221, \"end\": 1226